      "description": "Phantom uses a confident, muted-violet interface language. Its pages feature a bright canvas with substantial rounded corners, lending a soft, approachable feel to components. Typography is clear and prominent, anchoring sections, while a spectrum of muted and vivid violet tones defines interactive elements and brand accents against a largely achromatic background. Functional elements like buttons feature a subtle, colored box shadow that deepens the visual hierarchy without heavy drop shadows.",
